Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle with Grimoire Heart continues \Non the guild's sacred ground, Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Gramps down and out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the rest of us are in desperate battles with \Nthe Lost Magic using 7 Kin of Purgatory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it's looking like the second \Nin command, Bluenote, is drawing near...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:19.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,During all this, a woman the spitting \Nimage of Ul appeared in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:55.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia and Gray-sama were \Nenemies when they first met,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,however fickle fate drew them near!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia chased after Gray-sama and fought \Ntogether with him at the Tower of Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then she was welcomed into \Nthe guild as a Fairy Tail Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, she'll be linked for \Neternity with Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this isn't the kind \Nof link she was thinking of!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears of Love and Vigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:43.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia, Gray, and my senses \Nare all linked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:49.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, no matter which one \Nof us dies, Gray will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Craziness...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:03:00.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that you'd die as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my conviction!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us can do nothing but die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And my feet are cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's senses are flowing into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what's doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I get stuck with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:54.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lose sight \Nof them because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems to be \Npressing against my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama's sense of touch, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's leaning his back against something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I am linked with Gray, I have \Nno need to fight anyone, anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do is kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not afraid of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Your own leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maguilty sense will link the pain, but \Nit can't link the injury itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:13.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to stop me is to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one special exception to this \Nmagic is that death itself is linked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lives of those that \Nhave been linked are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you still plan on fighting it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:33.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only path we three have left is to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of us can live!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when defeating our opponents, Fairy \NTail wizards do not take their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naive fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to kill Gray for Ultear's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as Juvia is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:01.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be out of commission soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:54.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should crush her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were ordered to wipe out all the people \Nin the land where Zeref's key is sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see how I was in the \Npast when I look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl can get close \Nto the depths of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul, why do you always seem lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, don't call me Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul is my mother... My dead mother's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you about it, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}my{\i0} mother, Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need such a big girl as my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have happiness, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have people precious to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:22.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just our senses that are \Nlinked, but our emotions, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:35.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia... will live, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will live for the people she loves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have love, you've \Ngot to keep on living!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:46.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I link my emotions any \Nmore with this woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:09.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tears of love and vigor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These feelings are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama will never run, nor hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The senses that were connected \Nto me have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the mark on my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've noticed already, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:38.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ultear, the daughter \Nof your teacher, Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is Ul's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:56.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She and Jellal betrayed the Magic Council, \Nand actually belonged to Grimoire Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:02.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you hate my guts, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:03.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to see you for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:46.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes from the Spirit World. \NYou look splendid, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some for me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, change your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like, shall I assist you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine! I'll change myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain isn't stopping, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Carla and Lily are okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We found our camp along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel and Mira are in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily said he was stopping there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:31.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:36.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart's ship is beyond \Nthere, by the eastern shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our camp, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:41.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think we should head there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana might be there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be for the best \Nfor us all to join together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:52.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:08.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do something about Grimoire \NHeart and Zeref, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop them from attacking \Nthe island, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:16.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then buy us some time, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Countin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:25.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know exactly how you're \Ngoing to manage to overcome this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:59.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul's death was not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:13.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was only protecting her pupils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think of it with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care what you think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't think Ul would be \Nproud of what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora was the reason \Nthat Ul gave up her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:49.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was Zeref who created \Nthat thing, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:55.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are going to use Zeref to create \Nsome nutty world that makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:05.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm trying to do is what my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what Ul wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we finally meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One with true strength, Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl? I finished her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:47.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Meldy has been defeated... Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that over half of the \N7 Kin of Purgatory would be cut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluenote...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Makarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:34.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only one I didn't want to use...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and the others are coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Lu-chan and Wendy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless something has happened, \NCarla should be leading them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot of injured here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were attacked by the \Nenemy, we'd be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They should also be bringing \Nthe wounded Master here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They even got the Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're never going to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we all work together, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up is important, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world we live in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there is something called an "insurmountable \Ndifference in strength".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:32.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My fragment... it's shaking in excitement...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:38.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Devouring all the fairies, not \Nleaving a single one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I support myself in battle mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Levy, Lily too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've all reached the \Nlimits of our magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get here, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:08.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dranbalt-san... Will he be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Cana as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did we get separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's at the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this magic power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:36.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it raining so hard only near him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My skin is all tingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:06.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:42.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a monster even worse than him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, the annoying one has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:52.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to interrupt my meal, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluenote has arrived, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This war is over, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This island will be left lifeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:26.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care about \NFairy Tail, or Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing here that I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the grave of Fairy Tail's \Nfounding Master, Mavis Vermilion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mavis's grave is before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally become S class!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally meet my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave is... shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I need to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:23:59.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:02.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I have a secret that \NI've never told you, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you won't get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:08.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see... I actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:10.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really won't get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you got angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Words Couldn't Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.07,0:24:19.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause you wouldn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret because it's \Nsomething I can't tell people!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you bring \Nit up in the first place?
